--- !u!114 &-4837788555522000543
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e5800231a05eaae43b00503881229245, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  originalLanguage: en
  translationSets:
  - counter: 14
    languageCode: en
    translations:
    - id: 0
      language: en
      text: Man
    - id: 1
      language: en
      text: I would help you but I have a family to support.
    - id: 2
      language: en
      text: Don't introduce yourself, you change so quickly that it's not worth remembering.
    - id: 3
      language: en
      text: I wish you the best, and the next one, and the next one.
    - id: 4
      language: en
      text: Guard
    - id: 5
      language: en
      text: Welcome traveler! My name is Totharial
    - id: 6
      language: en
      text: Welcome traveler! My name is Totharial and I will help you with game,
        I mean your adventure.
    - id: 7
      language: en
      text: Totharial
    - id: 8
      language: en
      text: Firstly, you have few minutes before night will come. Days in our town
        are very short. You will have to fight with hordes of monsters.
    - id: 9
      language: en
      text: It will be opportunity for you to find supplies and villagers.
    - id: 10
      language: en
      text: 'The most important thing about nights - the longer you fight, the more
        powerful monsters appear. '
    - id: 11
      language: en
      text: They will be faster and stronger so don't be too long outside village.
    - id: 12
      language: en
      text: So how do you get back to the city? Find the portal that will take you
        back and let you end the night.
    - id: 13
      language: en
      text: Don't worry about the people you find, they'll handle it.
